Avoiding the area with ashtrays where smokers occasionally gather, I head for the edge of the roof.[l][r]
I put my hands on the railing, operate the device with my sweaty hands, and open the email I just forwarded.[r]
First, I needed to call. I tap the call button.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

