"Chito? Is it really you?!"[r]
I shouted.[r]
"Yeah, it's me. I'm so glad... Ishii, you also came to this world..."[l][r]
She was undoubtedly referring to this modern society as "this world." Her voice trembled as if she were on the verge of tears.[l][r]
"Yes, it's me. Ishii. I'm so glad. I never thought the day would come when I could speak with you again. I didn't think it was possible."[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

