[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
"Yeah... yes... wait. Just..."[r]
Chito interrupted, her voice sounding like she was trying to hold back sobs.[l][r]
"Oh... sorry. Let's take it easy," I said, trying to calm down both Chito and myself.[r]
"Yeah..."[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

